  "reference_number": "BEL0018",
  "remarks": "\nVasilieu was Head of the Department of Internal Affairs of Gomel Oblast Executive Committee.  In his former role as Department Head, Vasilieu was responsible for the actions of police officers in Gomel, including the Public Security Police and OMON riot police.  Vasilieu therefore bears responsibility for the serious human rights violations carried out by police officers following the election of 9 August, in particular arbitrary arrests and ill‐treatment, including torture, of peaceful demonstrators. \n",
